{"tid":2498682,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「選委會」第三界別新增同鄉社團　誠哥「潮屬社團總會」落選","createTime":"2021-04-21T10:26:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T10:41:44.000Z","uid":261647,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"90a54e796de2eff5b5901d499f5033eb73cadcb0","tid":2498682,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:26:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cantonese.rfa/posts/5327941840613624\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcantonese.rfa%2Fposts%2F5327941840613624&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dOSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=863ac920\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cantonese.rfa/posts/5327941840613624</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeowpwyeALTaQdVea86QX5fXARzDXLeur58Ga2XBEpcnM?filename=BMRhnC9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBMRhnC9.jpg&h=872c86e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：自由亞洲粵語 RFA Cantonese<br />\n<br />\n【「選委會」第三界別新增同鄉社團 】<br />\n【誠哥「潮屬社團總會」落選】<br />\n<br />\n港府推出草案修改香港選舉制度，負責產生特首的「選舉委員會」亦出現大洗牌。有親建制港媒報道，建制派出亦出現矛盾，原因是在「選委會」第三界別新增的「同鄉社團」，轄下有42個屬會及十幾萬會員的「潮屬社團總會」並沒有入圍。過去被視為香港「造王者」之一的香港首富李嘉誠，更是該會的首席名譽會長。<br />\n<br />\n香港特首林鄭月娥曾表示，今次訂定「選委會」團體選民，其中一個標準，是要有三年歷史，以避免種票。但在入圍的24個社團名單中，香港山東社團總會於2021年4月12日才成立，香港甘肅聯誼會則在2019年6月10日才成立。"},{"pid":"c9235e9cd9fac5c6612cb7198932f8e5dd146a19","tid":2498682,"uid":20170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:33:55.000Z","msg":"山東、甘肅都有位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔差在加埋陝西、貴州啦"},{"pid":"d6511b2f6df0f42383d0ada43d3990fd78ce51ce","tid":2498682,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9235e9cd9fac5c6612cb7198932f8e5dd146a19","tid":2498682,"uid":20170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:33:55.000Z","msg":"山東、甘肅都有位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔差在加埋陝西、貴州啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:37:16.000Z","msg":"呢樣真"},{"pid":"37804dcb180b2256d93681a6ced67a9b8fa16a99","tid":2498682,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:38:46.000Z","msg":"越嚟越似選黑幫坐館"},{"pid":"af4cce5af6b04dad8aadb12580d8c6c2b93624e6","tid":2498682,"uid":247211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37804dcb180b2256d93681a6ced67a9b8fa16a99","tid":2498682,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:38:46.000Z","msg":"越嚟越似選黑幫坐館"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:40:01.000Z","msg":"根本係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21b9b1038bc3e23bcf528d78ecb54784593ef0cd","tid":2498682,"uid":33352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:40:49.000Z","msg":"要有三年歷史，以避免種票。但在入圍的24個社團名單中，香港山東社團總會於<span class=\"red\">2021年4月12日</span>才成立，香港甘肅聯誼會則在2019年6月10日才成立。<br />\n<br />\n7婆: 總之我話佢夠就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n成立左幾日都批<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"247834eaa89974ee46bfe9652896ae51129c65a0","tid":2498682,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:41:27.000Z","msg":"誠哥呢啲有文化有學識嘅人上唔到去，係咪想元朗國班人上去"},{"pid":"aeff110753eb3f522a7100284c64564a206b1698","tid":2498682,"uid":17443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37804dcb180b2256d93681a6ced67a9b8fa16a99","tid":2498682,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:38:46.000Z","msg":"越嚟越似選黑幫坐館"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:41:44.000Z","msg":"重溫 黑社會 幾套電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}